00:01:27.540 --> 00:01:31.444
=The Maid=

00:01:31.444 --> 00:01:34.560
=Episode 15=

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:49.760
Shen Yuqing.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:52.240
You didn't anticipate this, right?

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:55.400
Li Si has long known your secret.

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:57.480
A replica was made.

00:02:14.675 --> 00:02:17.856
(Birth characters)

00:02:20.256 --> 00:02:21.728
(Qin Xiaoniang,
Shen Yuqing, Lin Jifu, Li Si)

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:33.344
(Lin Jifu)

00:02:42.323 --> 00:02:44.192
(Lin Jifu)

00:02:46.336 --> 00:02:48.576
(Lin Jifu)

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:04.200
You two stay.

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:05.560
Everyone else, out!

00:03:16.724 --> 00:03:20.416
(Virtuous Fragrance)

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:30.240
(Stepmother,)

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.680
(truth cannot be suppressed.)

00:03:33.480 --> 00:03:35.720
(You won't escape this time.)

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:41.960
(Don't cry.)

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:44.640
(We'll)

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:47.616
(stay with you.)

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.960
How heartless you all are.

00:04:15.600 --> 00:04:18.040
I bore Fu for ten long months

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:20.520
and defied the world
to bring her into it.

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:22.320
You murdered her

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.240
and trapped her spirit here

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:25.080
to suppress it,

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:27.160
denying her reincarnation!

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:29.560
Your Grace, you misspeak.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:31.400
Lin Jifu

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:34.400
is my distant cousin's daughter.

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.830
What connection does she have with you?

00:04:36.830 --> 00:04:38.880
Don't sacrifice greater gains
for trivial matters.

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:42.520
You dare threaten me?

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:45.760
I know my sins are grave.

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:48.000
Yet I've served you diligently

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:49.400
for years.

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:50.720
Though lacking merits,

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.640
I worked hard.

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:53.280
Moreover,

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.520
Fu died within Prince Regent's Mansion.

00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:58.840
How could Jin and I

00:04:59.280 --> 00:05:00.440
conceal such matters alone?

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:06.640
Do those who just provoked the incident

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.880
serve Pei Ji?

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:11.120
Exactly.

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:12.120
Your Grace,

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.640
this is clearly a plotted scheme.

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:15.000
Now,

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.080
my father's Western Army

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.696
has gained formidable power

00:05:17.696 --> 00:05:18.976
through my marriage with Pei Ji.

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:20.800
Wouldn't abandoning us

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.400
mean forsaking the Duke's Mansion

00:05:24.056 --> 00:05:25.056
and weakening your power?

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:33.640
Truly my dear sister

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:36.920
and precious niece.

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:49.680
Rise.

00:05:50.960 --> 00:05:52.200
Duchess.

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.840
Princess Consort.

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.840
It seems that you two
silver-tongued women

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:08.040
have clearly planned every detail.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.560
What comes next

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:11.280
in your plan?

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:13.400
I

00:06:13.880 --> 00:06:16.240
have a plan
to achieve two goals at once.

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:33.720
The climate's arid.

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:36.000
Beware of accidental fires.

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:46.760
Please reconsider.

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:48.520
Within these walls,

00:06:48.920 --> 00:06:49.840
lie remnants of those

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.120
wronged by Madam Su.

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:52.840
Their deaths were tragic enough.

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:54.800
Burning this place would deny

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:55.872
countless spirits

00:06:55.872 --> 00:06:57.120
their eternal rest.

00:06:57.220 --> 00:06:57.840
Your Grace,

00:06:58.480 --> 00:07:00.160
my mother's ornaments remain inside.

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:01.680
She once performed for you.

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:03.280
The ornaments were gifts from you.

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:05.480
But later, Father forced her
to be his concubine.

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.680
Stepmother framed her for adultery.

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.280
And my newborn child...

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:10.680
Madam Su drowned him

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:11.720
with breastmilk...

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:12.440
Shut up!

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:17.080
Please reconsider, Your Grace.

00:07:17.824 --> 00:07:19.080
Please hold justice for us.

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:21.000
Please show us your mercy.

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:23.400
Please show us your mercy.

00:07:23.960 --> 00:07:26.080
Please show us your mercy.

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:27.200
Your Grace,

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:29.680
Jifu remains inside.

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.040
She said

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:33.480
she loathed full moons.

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:35.200
No family ties,

00:07:35.400 --> 00:07:36.600
exiled by marriage,

00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:38.320
smiling through the pain.

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:40.160
Only when drunk would she

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:41.560
cling to my hand

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:42.680
and murmur.

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:43.800
She said,

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:44.960
"Mother,

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:46.400
I'll obey.

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:48.880
Don't abandon me, okay?"

00:08:02.280 --> 00:08:03.040
Your Grace,

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.840
don't be swayed by schemers.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.162
What are you waiting for?

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.480
Get her!

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:11.328
Your Grace.

00:08:12.640 --> 00:08:13.760
- Go away!
- Go away!

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:16.120
Your Grace.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:20.320
Dare cause trouble
at the Duke's Mansion?

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:21.960
I'll use this chaos

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:24.280
to burn you alive too.

00:09:21.460 --> 00:09:23.136
(Virtuous Fragrance)

00:09:34.120 --> 00:09:35.600
The investigation remains incomplete.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.240
Trying to destroy evidence already?

00:09:37.560 --> 00:09:38.560
Pei Ji,

00:09:38.920 --> 00:09:40.360
how dare you

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:42.280
offend me?

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:43.800
By the laws,

00:09:44.064 --> 00:09:45.120
no one is above the law,

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.240
even the emperor.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:48.960
Do you intend to shield your own sister?

00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:49.952
You...

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:52.560
Guards!

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:55.488
Take Madam Su for interrogation.

00:09:55.488 --> 00:09:56.192
- Understood!
- Understood!

00:09:58.720 --> 00:09:59.480
Your Grace,

00:09:59.560 --> 00:10:00.680
please save my mother.

00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:04.920
Must you escalate matters to this point

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:06.680
before confessing the truth?

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:07.640
Too late.

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:17.880
Your Highness,

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:18.960
she is my mother,

00:10:18.960 --> 00:10:20.080
your mother-in-law,

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.160
and a first-rank Duchess!

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:25.800
Jin,

00:10:26.784 --> 00:10:27.904
you're the Princess Consort.

00:10:28.128 --> 00:10:29.320
Even under crushing pressure,

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:31.320
a Princess Consort
must keep her composure.

00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:33.280
Fulfill your duties.

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:34.560
Let go of me!

00:10:35.280 --> 00:10:37.080
I'll walk on my own.

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:48.040
Escort the Princess Consort
to the mansion.

00:11:04.576 --> 00:11:05.344
Your Highness.

00:11:08.224 --> 00:11:09.760
We should return now.

00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:35.360
You played an excellent move.

00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:37.800
(First, you used Concubine Ye)

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:40.160
(to plant that rhyme
in the Empress Dowager's ear.)

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:44.600
Then you staged a heroic rescue.

00:11:44.690 --> 00:11:47.130
It severed Empress Dowager's alliance
with the Duke's Mansion,

00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:48.920
cutting off her power,

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:50.800
while winning you the beauty's heart.

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:53.760
She offered the blade,

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:54.720
and I sheathed it.

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:56.920
A meeting of equals.

00:12:17.440 --> 00:12:20.000
This perilla tea and plum cake

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:21.440
were prepared by me.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:24.040
Please have a taste.

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:52.840
Your Highness,

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:55.680
beautiful women ruin nations.

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:57.040
Don't indulge.

00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:12.480
My lady,

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:14.160
how did you know he'd help us?

00:13:15.080 --> 00:13:17.160
The Empress Dowager
and Prince Regent rule jointly.

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:19.120
But it's merely temporary.

00:13:20.040 --> 00:13:21.160
No people serve two rulers.

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:22.720
No nation has two monarchs.

00:13:23.480 --> 00:13:25.720
They both seek each other's demise.

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:28.200
Pei Ji would never pass up

00:13:28.760 --> 00:13:30.920
such a chance
to weaken the Empress Dowager.

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:34.600
I don't understand.

00:13:34.920 --> 00:13:36.280
Didn't he allow them

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:37.640
to cover up Lin Jifu's death?

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:41.240
That's because Lin Jifu

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:42.920
was truly killed by Shen Yuanjin.

00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:45.280
Shen Yuanjin is the Princess Consort

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:47.600
and Zhao's mother.

00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:54.840
Now that blame shifts to Madam Su,

00:13:55.400 --> 00:13:57.520
the Prince Regent's Mansion
escapes suspicion.

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:00.720
Madam Su

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:03.240
truly needs to be dealt with.

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:31.160
Coming to mock me?

00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:33.080
Aren't you early for the show?

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:35.400
You seem confident

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.840
that you'll emerge unscathed again?

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:41.920
I have the Empress Dowager

00:14:42.640 --> 00:14:43.760
and the Duke's Mansion.

00:14:44.640 --> 00:14:46.000
Even if convicted,

00:14:46.960 --> 00:14:49.200
I'll only stay in temple estates

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:51.560
or at manors for a while.

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:53.240
Once the storm passes,

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.520
I shall return.

00:15:04.880 --> 00:15:05.960
Once I leave this cell,

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:08.120
I'll end you.

00:15:08.760 --> 00:15:09.880
My lady,

00:15:09.880 --> 00:15:11.040
you're correct.

00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:13.960
The Empress Dowager
indeed won't investigate

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:15.000
Lin Jifu's death.

00:15:15.520 --> 00:15:16.600
She even proclaims

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:20.200
she personally witnessed
the coroner's examination.

00:15:22.080 --> 00:15:23.240
All these years,

00:15:23.712 --> 00:15:27.080
how many innocent souls
has the Duke's Mansion condemned?

00:15:27.240 --> 00:15:28.240
Concubines,

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:29.120
concubine-born sons

00:15:29.880 --> 00:15:30.880
and daughters...

00:15:31.280 --> 00:15:34.200
Need I list them all?

00:15:35.168 --> 00:15:36.960
The Duke covered for you,

00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:39.360
calling them mere accidents.

00:15:41.640 --> 00:15:43.040
Are you here to plead for peace?

00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:48.720
Among those keepsakes,

00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:52.400
some are former belongings
of noblewomen from the capital.

00:15:53.520 --> 00:15:54.800
I wonder if you

00:15:55.560 --> 00:15:57.040
still remember

00:15:58.200 --> 00:16:01.320
the wife of Director Ma
from the Guanglu Court?

00:16:02.320 --> 00:16:03.400
What do you mean?

00:16:04.760 --> 00:16:07.200
Director Ma served
three successive reigns.

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:09.880
He used to oversee
the enthronement ceremony.

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:11.392
He once advised

00:16:11.392 --> 00:16:13.190
that the Emperor's ascension
was illegitimate.

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:15.880
This ritual critique
offended the Empress Dowager.

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:17.200
Later,

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:19.200
due to his wife's accidental death,

00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:20.960
he became overwhelmed with grief

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.240
and retired to his hometown.

00:16:23.200 --> 00:16:24.360
But recently,

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.160
his youngest son

00:16:28.600 --> 00:16:30.920
was appointed as Director of Dali Court.

00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:34.320
He still holds great influence at court

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:37.160
and the enthronement controversy
remains relevant.

00:16:38.440 --> 00:16:39.200
The Empress Dowager

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:41.840
has delegated full authority
to Dali Court.

00:16:42.520 --> 00:16:45.280
The Duke has also severed ties with you.

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:47.520
Impossible!

00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:49.200
How dare you spread lies!

00:16:49.400 --> 00:16:50.560
I'll tear your mouth apart!

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:58.520
Stepmother,

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:01.520
I've schemed for three years

00:17:02.640 --> 00:17:04.400
just for this moment.

00:17:08.200 --> 00:17:10.520
You truly are Shen Yuqing.

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:12.280
Guards!

00:17:12.560 --> 00:17:13.280
Guards!

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:14.400
Guards!

00:17:21.840 --> 00:17:23.240
You murdered imperial kin,

00:17:23.840 --> 00:17:25.360
which is also a capital offense.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:27.680
Stepmother,

00:17:28.640 --> 00:17:29.880
you taught me

00:17:30.800 --> 00:17:32.760
to destroy both body and spirit.

00:17:34.304 --> 00:17:35.440
Someone else

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:37.720
will come claim your life.

00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:43.480
I

00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:48.320
merely came to offer you wine.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:00.960
Does it hurt?

00:18:01.880 --> 00:18:02.760
It's just right.

00:18:03.280 --> 00:18:04.480
What you're enduring

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:05.760
is but a fraction of the pain

00:18:05.760 --> 00:18:07.360
my mother and I suffered!

00:18:45.812 --> 00:18:50.553
♪I once fell into deep love♪

00:18:52.033 --> 00:18:56.713
♪Caught in a drama of love and hate♪

00:18:57.873 --> 00:18:59.953
♪Trapped in self-made cages♪

